## Dependencyes
- we use uv as dependecy handler
- Do not install packages on your own use `uv sync` instead
    - Do not use `uv pip install`

## No Legacy / backwards compatibility
- This is the only copy of this project therefore we do not need ANY kind of backwards compatibility or legacy checks
- If there is something new everything should assume the old one was never there in the first place.
- THe policy is no legacy code. Remove everything unused, archiving is done via git.

## Tests
- we do NOT do test driven development. 
    - Tests should be adapted to changes.
    - don't assume something should be like that only because an old test asserts it
- Do only write tests when useful.
    - minor scripts do not need tests.